<title type="html"><![CDATA[1/4(Sat.)Eliminate Procrastination With This Simple Technique/Google — Year in Search 2019(Host: Danny)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=350&amp;p=366#p366"><![CDATA[
1/4(Sat.)If You’re Planning A Big Goal In 2020, Eliminate Procrastination With This Simple Technique/Google — Year in Search 2019(Host: Danny)<br /><br />Article 1: If You’re Planning A Big Goal In 2020, Eliminate Procrastination With This Simple Technique<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/markmurphy/2019/12/05/if-youre-planning-a-big-goal-in-2020-eliminate-procrastination-with-this-simple-technique/#2e36f3583797">https://www.forbes.com/sites/markmurphy ... 36f3583797</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />1. Would you like to share the new goal in the new year? <br />2. Have you achieved the goal last year? Why or why not? <br />3. Do you have procrastination problems? if not, please read the next question.<br />4. Or you have some tips to solve them. Please share that with us.<br /><br />Article 2:Google — Year in Search 2019<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZRCdORJiUgU">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZRCdORJiUgU</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />1. Who is your Hero in 2019? Please share that even a virtual one.<br />2. Are you a Hero to anyone? ( You must a hero in your family, company or school. Please share your story. )<br />3. &quot; To everyone using their powers to empower others.&quot; Do you think you can do more in this year? Perhaps it is time to modify your goals~<br /><br />Bonus film:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2lAe1cqCOXo (YouTube Rewind 2019: For the Record | #YouTubeRewind)<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Tue Dec 31, 2019 2:43 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
